imdb.title: diMartedì
plot: Italian prime-time news program and political talk show broadcast by LA7 television on Tuesday evenings. Created and hosted by journalist Giovanni Floris, who also invented "Ballarò". Comedian Maurizio Crozza opens each episode.::Oops!
